"},"$:/plugins/wikilabs/click-effect/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/wikilabs/click-effect/readme","caption":"Click Effect","tags":"$:/tags/ControlPanel/WikiLabs","text":"The full documentation can be found at [[click-effect plugin|https://wikilabs.github.io/editions/click-effect/]] main page.

! Basics

This plugin shows a little "click animation" if the left mouse button is released

! Settings

Th current setting is: ''{{$:/config/clickEffect}}''

| Setting | Description |h
|<$radio field="text" tiddler="$:/config/clickEffect" value="clickEffect"> Click Effect</$radio> |A little click animation is shown at the cursor position |
|<$radio field="text" tiddler="$:/config/clickEffect" value="pulse"> Element Pulse</$radio> |The html-element, that is clicked is highlighted |
|<$radio field="text" tiddler="$:/config/clickEffect" value="no"> Off</$radio> |No click-animaiton is shown|

----

''Important'': This plugin modifies several core modules

